node.text: In honor of Breast Cancer Awareness month, we brought together breast cancer thrivers and healthcare heroes for a socially distanced shoot to share their stories. We put our paws up in honor of these inspiring women! We acknowledge there are many stories to tell and sadly many who aren’t here to tell theirs. Our campaign this month shares who YOU put your paws up in honor of and pays tribute to all those  impacted by breast cancer.

node.title: Introducing Our Newest Print with Purpose in Support of BCRF

node.text: A few months ago, we launched “Magical Mary,” a Lilly Pulitzer & Make-a-Wish print with purpose created by our friend Mary and benefiting the Children’s Hospital of Philadelphia. Inspired by her favorite animal, the unicorn, Mary chose to have her print made into a few styles including a girls popover and a girls Harper Shift...which quickly sold out! We are happy to announce that due to high demand, we have restocked the girls popover and shift dress! Yes. Way. Shop now.

node.title: Lilly Pulitzer Print with Purpose: Magical Mary

node.text: #regram @amandakloots: "’When you can't find the sunshine, be the sunshine.’ For me, fashion is more than getting dressed--it's a chance to show my optimistic style through what I choose. And today I choose the Katalina Midi Eyelet Dress from @lillypulitzer's Endless Summer collection. Lilly's iconic resortwear, happy colors, chic styles, and sunny side up outlook on life resonates with me and I think you'll love it too.” #lillypulitzer #endlesssummer #linkinprofile
